<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('./partials/head') %>
  <title>Privacy Policy · ProjectMate</title>
</head>
<body class="pm-body">
  <div class="pm-grid-overlay"></div>
  
  <%- include('./partials/navbar') %>

  <main class="pm-page" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 1.5rem;">
    <h1 class="pm-hero-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="pm-hero-subtitle" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">Last updated: March 17, 2026</p>

    <div style="line-height: 1.8; color: var(--pm-subtext);">
      <h2 style="color: var(--pm-text); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">1. Introduction</h2>
      <p>ProjectMate ("we," "us," "our," or "Company") operates the ProjectMate website and application. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information.</p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--pm-text); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">2. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, bio, profile picture, portfolio links, and project history.</p>
      <p><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Pages visited, time spent, search queries, clicks, and device information.</p>
      <p><strong>Communication Data:</strong> Messages between users (stored securely on our servers).</p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--pm-text); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul style="margin-left: 2rem;">
        <li>Provide and improve our services</li>
        <li>Process transactions and send confirmations</li>
        <li>Send emails about account updates</li>
        <li>Respond to inquiries and support requests</li>
        <li>Enforce our Terms of Service</li>
        <li>Prevent fraud and ensure security</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="color: var(--pm-text); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">4. Data Security</h2>
      <p>We use industry-standard encryption (HTTPS/SSL) and bcrypt hashing for passwords. However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure. We cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--pm-text); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">5. Your Rights (GDPR & CCPA)</h2>
      <p><strong>You have the right to:</strong></p>
      <ul style="margin-left: 2rem;">
        <li>Access your personal data</li>
        <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Opt-out of marketing communications</li>
        <li>Request a data portability report</li>
      </ul>

      <p>To exercise these rights, contact us at privacy@projectmate.com</p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--pm-text); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">6. Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use cookies to authenticate users and store preferences. You can disable cookies in your browser settings, but some features may not work properly.</p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--pm-text); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">7. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We may use third-party services for analytics, hosting, and payments. These services have their own privacy policies.</p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--pm-text); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy occasionally. We will notify you of changes by updating the "Last updated" date.</p>

      <h2 style="color: var(--pm-text); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">9. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:</p>
      <p>
        <strong>Email:</strong> privacy@projectmate.com<br>
        <strong>Website:</strong> www.projectmate.com
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <%- include('./partials/footer') %>
  <%- include('./partials/scripts') %>
</body>
</html>
